nodes.text: Henshin was a Zabrak male Jedi Master serving the Jedi Order and the  Galactic Republic. Henshin was stationed on Taris during the Cold War.
Henshin was originally set to appear in the  video game Star Wars: The Old Republic but for whatever reason his character was cut before release. Henshin's file can be found on Jedipedia.
